data.description: Welcome to 10 acres of beautifully treed land accompanied by a charming 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom house. This exquisite estate offers a serene and spacious environment, combining the allure of countryside living with modern comfort. The house boasts three generously-sized bedrooms, providing ample room for family, guests, or creating personalized spaces such as a home office or hobby room. Stepping outside you can experience the luxury of ample space with 10 acres of versatile land, providing endless possibilities for your dreams and aspirations. This property is perfect for those seeking a private retreat, agricultural ventures, or simply enjoying the beauty of nature.
